    "description": "本課程主要介紹近年極受重視之通用設計概念，並配合設計討論及各國之實際產品說明，使選修學生能充分了解其理念，提升其設計能力。<br>This course introduces the universal design concepts that have been highly valued in recent years, and cooperates with design discussions to enable elective students to fully understand UD concepts and enhance their design capabilities.<br><br>",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "透過以下各單元之介紹，培養修課同學對於UD設計理念之深入瞭解及實際應用於設計之能力。<br>1.發展背景<br>2.定義<br>3.UD七大基本原則<br>4.UD三附則<br>5.範例介紹<br>6.實際設計操作與討論<br><br>",
        "en": "Through the introduction of the following units, the students will be trained to understand the UD design concept and the practical application of the design.<br>1. Development background<br>2. Definition<br>3. UD seven basic principles<br>4.UD three attachments<br>5. Introduction to the sample<br>6. Actual design operation and discussion<br>"
